Package: DTRAC
Title: A Rule-Based Classifier for Difficult-to-Treat Rheumatoid Arthritis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "RS", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a tool for the stratification of patients with Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA). It implements a deterministic, rule-based algorithm that uses a series of logical conditions and matrix manipulations to classify patients as 'Difficult-to-Treat' (D2T).
